HEADWORD: Straightforward
<hw>Straight`for"ward</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Proceeding
in a straight course or manner; not deviating; honest; frank.</def> --
<def2><pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a straightforward manner.</def></def2> --
<wordforms><wf>Straight`for"ward*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Straight`for"ward*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Straighthorn</ent>⟦br⟧
